{"tid":2216602,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"HA重啟清算罷工醫護 大家會”撐手足 撐到底”嗎?","createTime":"2020-09-24T23:09:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T04:45:44.000Z","uid":123774,"like":29,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"63aafc054e5dc06e4075f7117207f9470fb8deec","tid":2216602,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T23:09:36.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>HA重啟清算罷工醫護 <br />\n漠視拒封關害百人命 攬炒經濟</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n記唔記得二月份香港人嘅情緒?<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>醫護罷工求封關救港</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pnTtQcs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpnTtQcs.jpg&h=2ba55715&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/asCKox6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FasCKox6.jpg&h=d9f355ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>黃藍不分 齊燒暉明邨</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z8s2UFK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ8s2UFK.jpg&h=5868d37f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sCcqSCp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsCcqSCp.jpg&h=bafb7ff1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>92籤威脅封關</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b2ET1wY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb2ET1wY.png&h=1b886e97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S3rvi8u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS3rvi8u.jpg&h=362a8e20&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eyMfvfa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeyMfvfa.jpg&h=be636441&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>幾千人通宵排隊買口罩</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hvkoEbo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhvkoEbo.jpg&h=690afbb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人話佢哋堅持唔夠耐 但事實係:<br />\n罷工需要長時間籌備 包括成立儲備基金<br />\n<br />\nHA利用醫護渡過頭兩波疫<br />\n一靜左 4月就過橋抽板請律師準備清算<br />\n到7月頭因豁免令再爆第三波<br />\nHA即刻縮手 再利用醫護<br />\n而家靜咗 HA又再次過橋抽板啟動清算<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4PH2UMu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4PH2UMu.jpg&h=3c774d7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n12個香港人被送終待遇<br />\n證明反送中係必須係正確<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎第三波係因為輕視封關<br />\n證明醫護罷工要求封關係正確<br />\n如果當初有聽專業意見封關<br />\n今日就唔會無辜犧牲做成百條人命<br />\n經濟唔會一潭死水 失業率創新高<br />\n<br />\n支共分明針對任何搞活動帶頭嘅人<br />\n希望大家唔好忘記醫護嘅付出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無Ching可以教路<br />\n要寫感謝信支持醫護應該寄去邊?"},{"pid":"9c85387b6daa674ec33078594731ac00cd8c82ae","tid":2216602,"uid":14494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T23:13:16.000Z","msg":"睇見正苦個齊心抗疫就覺得嘔心"},{"pid":"6bea906f2944caea48dd9732ee14b32325073cd8","tid":2216602,"uid":67049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T23:14:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a34512918f38e4d4522ff6e763298da415de7013","tid":2216602,"uid":67049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T23:14:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"db92771ab0fcf8be977155f2937bee0452c037d6","tid":2216602,"uid":225540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T23:15:02.000Z","msg":"希望只係做下樣<br />\n真清算就大撚鑊"},{"pid":"989d54dd535a64e7d1e8d2ac1d5736ab21941b8c","tid":2216602,"uid":67049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T23:16:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5784d28d299c2b5262a550096ef27cd87dab2625","tid":2216602,"uid":123774,